sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant LlamaStack as LlamaStack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant KubeRBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event notification<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update managed resources<br/>(Deployment, Service, PVC, NetworkPolicy,<br/>Ingress, HPA, PDB, SA, ConfigMap)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>LlamaStack: Health check GET /v1/health<br/>8321/TCP HTTP, No Auth
    LlamaStack-->>Controller: Health status response
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update LlamaStackDistribution status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 2: ConfigMap Change Propagation

    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (ConfigMap change)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment pod annotation<br/>(triggers rolling restart)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>LlamaStack: Pod rolling restart

    Note over Prometheus,KubeRBACProxy: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>KubeRBACProxy: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    KubeRBACProxy->>Controller: Forward to 8080/TCP<br/>HTTP localhost, No Auth
    Controller-->>KubeRBACProxy: Metrics response
    KubeRBACProxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics (HTTPS)
